WEBVTT

00:12:57.416 --> 00:13:02.138
And once again, I was
an angry black woman.

00:13:02.138 --> 00:13:05.313
I went home and I said to my mom,

00:13:05.313 --> 00:13:09.807
"Your act, your action,
no matter what your may defense may be" --

00:13:09.807 --> 00:13:12.401
because she thought she did it out love --

00:13:12.401 --> 00:13:17.029
"what you did out of love 
is harming me, and it's hurting me.

00:13:17.029 --> 00:13:20.851
What do you have to say for that?"

00:13:20.851 --> 00:13:24.035
She said, "I did what I had to do
as a mother."

00:13:24.035 --> 00:13:26.744
I'm still waiting
for an apology, by the way.

00:13:28.124 --> 00:13:30.511
Then I got married.